headline: onsemi to Announce Fourth Quarter and 2024 Annual Financial Results
summary: SCOTTSDALE, Ariz., January 23, 2025--onsemi (Nasdaq: ON) plans to announce its financial results for the fourth quarter and full year, which ended December 31, 2024, before the market opens on Monday, February 10, 2025.
